he world to use recycled fabrics on october   the gores group received private equity internationals award for operational excellence in the tmt sector for lineage power pei’s operational excellence awards recognize and highlight the achievements in the industry on june   the gores group won the global ma networks atlas award for turnaround deal of the year for their acquisition of national envelope corporation on december   the gores group was named the winner of the middlemarket deal of the year award – million for their acquisition of cosmo specialty fibers at the th annual ma advisor awards the gores group was selected from  nominations and over  participating companies to receive this award representative transactionsedit january   the gores group announced that it has reached a conditional agreement with premier foods to operate its bread business as a standalone venture under the name of hovis limited in order to increase operational efficiencies and grow the hovis brand august   stock building supply holdings inc nasdaqstck announced that it has closed its previously announced underwritten initial public offering of  shares of common stock at the price to the public of  per share the underwriters exercised in their full option to purchase an additional  shares of common stock from certain selling stockholders resulting in a total initial public offering size of  shares july   gores’ portfolio company the hay group announced that it had entered into an agreement to acquire metallumform an integrated manufacturer of forged machined automotive components with two plants in germany terms of the transaction were not disclosed january   the gores group announced that it had completed the acquisition of therakos inc from orthoclinical diagnostics inc december   charles bank capital partners announced that it acquired united road services from the gores group for an undisclosed amount kathleen mccann president and ceo will continue to lead the company october   the 